# Rakune! 
## Copy. Paste. Remember (Your Code!)

### DEMO!
[Click here for demo!](http://sixteenink.com/eatpaste)

### Rakune! 
Now you can host your paste bin on your own website in minutes. 

### How do I do?
Simply install, click the add new button and paste your code snippet!

### Is this open source? 
YUP! Send me a pull request to contribute. I would be happy to look at any pull request!

### I'm in, how can I help?
Rakune was written in CakePHP. So extending it is easy! Check out the issues section to see bugs and features!

### License?
Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 Unported License. Meaning, build and share! I don't care!
